==English==

===Etymology===
From the city of Shergotty India, where the first specimen was found in 1865.

===Pronunciation===
*IPA: [[WEAE]] /ˌʃɚ.gəˈtaɪt/
*SAMPA: /%S@g@"taIt/

===Noun===
'''shergottite'''
